Out of curiosity, I reached out to Carrie Keranen who is the voice of LeBlanc and Lux about her current work with Riot on the Lux Voice Update and Legendary Skin.

I asked, &quot;...Would you ever possibly return to Riot for a LeBlanc skin that has new voice lines?!&quot;

Keranen replies, &quot;If they ever asked I would for sure!!!&quot;

